OL,3,CVoltage surge caused power cut that
OL,4,Cplunged Spain and Portugal into
OL,5,Cdarkness
OL,7,FShe ruled out that the failure was due
OL,8,Fto a cyberattack.
OL,10,FOn April 28, around 60% of Spain's
OL,11,Felectricity was lost in the major
OL,12,Fblackout, disrupting businesses,
OL,13,Ftransport systems, mobile networks,
OL,14,Finternet connectivity and other
OL,15,Fcritical infrastructure. Portugal,
OL,16,Fwhose grid is connected to Spain's,
OL,17,Falso went down.
OL,19,F"All of this happened in 12 seconds,
OL,20,Fwith most of the power loss happening
OL,21,Fin just five seconds," Aagesen said.
