OL,3,CVoltage surge caused power cut that
OL,4,Cplunged Spain and Portugal into
OL,5,Cdarkness
OL,7,FSeveral technical causes contributed
OL,8,Fto the event, including "poor
OL,9,Fplanning" by Spain's grid operator Red
OL,10,FElectrica, which didn't find a
OL,11,Freplacement for one power plant that
OL,12,Fwas supposed to help balance power
OL,13,Ffluctuations, the minister said.
OL,15,FShe also said that some power plants
OL,16,Fthat utilities shut off preventively
OL,17,Fwhen the disruptions started could
OL,18,Fhave stayed online to help manage the
OL,19,Fsystem.
