OL,7,FThe Red Electrica is yet to respond to
OL,8,Fthe government's claims.
OL,10,FThe blackout caused a national
OL,11,Femergency in Spain as a day of
OL,12,Fwidespread disruption saw cities
OL,13,Fgridlocked, commuters trapped inside
OL,14,Ftrains and flights grounded.
OL,16,FThere were also reports of medical
OL,17,Fservices implementing emergency plans
OL,18,Fto mitigate the impact on the
OL,19,Fhealthcare system.
