OL,7,FIn the weeks following the blackout,
OL,8,Fthe outage ignited a fierce debate
OL,9,Fabout whether Spain's high levels of
OL,10,Frenewable power and not enough energy
OL,11,Fgenerated from nuclear or gas-fired
OL,12,Fpower plants had something to do with
OL,13,Fthe grid failing, which the government
OL,14,Fhas repeatedly denied.
