OL,7,FSpain is at the forefront of Europe's
OL,8,Ftransition to renewable energy, having
OL,9,Fgenerated nearly 57% of its
OL,10,Felectricity in 2024 from renewable
OL,11,Fenergy sources like wind, hydropower
OL,12,Fand solar. The country is also phasing
OL,13,Fout its nuclear plants.
