OL,7,FSpanish Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez
OL,8,Fpushed back against such speculation
OL,9,Fand defended the country's rapid
OL,10,Framping up of renewables. He asked for
OL,11,Fpatience and said that his government
OL,12,Fwould not "deviate a single
OL,13,Fmillimeter" from its energy transition
OL,14,Fplans, which include a goal of
OL,15,Fgenerating 81% of its electricity from
OL,16,Frenewable sources by 2030.
